# Infra Local

**Fonte:** `README.md` · `docker-compose.yml` · `docker/`

---

## Portas

| Serviço | Porta | Acesso |
|---------|-------|--------|
| Kong | `8000` | `http://localhost:8000/games/*` · `/wallets/*` |
| Game | `4001` | direto ou via Kong |
| Wallet | `4002` | direto ou via Kong |
| PostgreSQL | `5432` | DBs `games`, `wallets` |
| LocalStack SQS | `4566` | edge API |
| Keycloak | `8080` | realm `crash-game` |
| Frontend | `3000` | quando scaffold existir |

**Eliminatório:** `bun run docker:up` sobe tudo sem passo manual (inclui filas SQS).

---

## Keycloak (dev)

- Realm `crash-game` · client `crash-game-client` (PKCE)
- Usuário teste: `player` / `player123`
- Import automático: `docker/keycloak/realm-export.json`

---

## Comandos

```bash
bun install && bun run docker:up
cp services/games/.env.example services/games/.env    # fora do Docker
cp services/wallets/.env.example services/wallets/.env
```

Health: `GET /health` em games e wallets (inclui `messaging`). Detalhes: `README.md`.
